<p>
	These lovely incense packs contain 40 highly fragranced sticks in each tin that burn for approximately&nbsp;40 minutes per stick. These sticks expertly capture the true essences of rose bergamot, ylang ylang and chocolate orange fragrances and leave a beautifully scented aroma. Simply light, place the stick into a holder and enjoy the aromas and feel the stress of modern living going up in smoke! Each incense stick is approx. 26cm long and the pack comes in an elegant golden metal box which is approx. 29cm tall and 4cm wide.</p>
